profile: Here at A Step Above, we specialize in manufacturing and installing custom stairs and railings. We also build and install all types of custom cabinetry and millwork, including kitchens, bars, wall-units, and store fixtures. These products are constructed using all types of woods, laminates, veneers, and solid surfaces. Our dedication to quality and on-time delivery is something our craftsmen pride themselves on. It would be our honour to help you design and build your dream home or cottage. A Step Above can also help you realize all your commercial requirements in these areas. For your benefit, we only use the finest handpicked materials. Our staircases and millwork are produced using only solid wood for everlasting beauty and reliability. The manufacturing facility is located in Gravenhurst, Ontario and services all of Muskoka, Ontario and the surrounding areas. It would be our genuine honour, through our design and construction process, to help you realize your vision.
